tweet: Look, let's be clear here: I am one of the @godsofTweetland. But unlike most of those guys, I'm a COOL Tweetish deity. Okay?
Feeling a touch neglected. Me, the chief among Tweet gods. No followers. And yet, above following others. Sigh.
Perhaps a ride on my thunder chariot? Hmm. Did I change that flat wheel last week?
It's hard to be this glorious. Seriously. Try it some time.
Radiating peace and love to all.
